    "en": {
      "title": "Notification of Motor Transport Department",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been announced that the Motor Vehicle Transport Department will not be open on Fridays of the week.",
        "According to a statement issued by the department, it will be closed on Fridays until further notice after the 15th.",
        "This decision has been taken due to the traffic problem caused by the inability to deliver fuel. (a)"
